<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed | SellYourCar.co.uk</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2d3748;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #56ab2f 0%, #a8e6cf 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 50px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transform: skewY(-2deg);
            transform-origin: top left;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-weight: 400;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 45px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0fff4 100%);
        }
        
        .content p {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .content p strong {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .success-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #56ab2f 0%, #a8e6cf 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(86, 171, 47, 0.3);
        }

        .disclaimer {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-top: 35px;
            border-top: 2px solid #c6f6d5;
            padding-top: 25px;
            background-color: #f0fff4;
            padding: 25px 20px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #56ab2f;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d3748 0%, #4a5568 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 20px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #56ab2f 0%, #a8e6cf 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 16px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 40px 20px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Password Updated! ✅</h1>
            <p>This is a security notification for your account.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Hello <%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %>,</strong></p>
            <div class="success-badge">✓ Password Successfully Changed</div>
            <p>This is to confirm that the password for your account has been successfully changed.</p>
            <p class="disclaimer">If you did not make this change, please contact us immediately to secure your account. Your security is our top priority.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="logo">SellYourCar</div>
            <p>Thank you for choosing our service</p>
            <p>Customer Service: admin@sellyourcar.info</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> sellyourcar.info All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>